♪In a flash, back to the past♪

2
00:00:33,810 --> 00:00:39,310
♪Your shadow appears so fast♪

3
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:41,680
♪Again and again♪

4
00:00:42,970 --> 00:00:45,520
♪Our warmth fades away♪

5
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:49,350
♪We're at the edge, no words to say♪

6
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:53,640
♪Cross the line, it's you and me♪

7
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:56,970
♪Softly saying goodbye, set free♪

8
00:00:57,640 --> 00:01:01,350
♪Walking paths we once knew♪

9
00:01:01,350 --> 00:01:04,770
♪Reliving sweet times with you♪

10
00:01:04,890 --> 00:01:11,810
♪But in your world, I was blank♪

11
00:01:11,810 --> 00:01:15,560
♪Through the crowd, I hug you tight♪

12
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:20,060
♪Like raindrops in the cool night♪

13
00:01:20,470 --> 00:01:24,640
♪Memories frozen, love so bright♪

14
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:28,600
♪I don't want to forget♪

15
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:31,930
♪Our light♪

16
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:39,680
[An adaptation from Eternal Love
by Ye Feiye from China Literature]

17
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:44,430
[101 Marriages]

18
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:47,430
[Episode 9]

19
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:54,160
Did everyone memorize the homework

20
00:01:54,330 --> 00:01:55,290
I gave yesterday?

21
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:56,700
It was "Memorial to Emperor".

22
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:59,160
She assigned it?

23
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,040
Gu Lanshan.

24
00:02:06,450 --> 00:02:07,330
Why don't you start?

25
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,120
The teacher's calling on you.

26
00:02:18,540 --> 00:02:19,790
The first line is...

27
00:02:21,950 --> 00:02:23,950
"The late Emperor began a great mission

28
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,910
but passed away before it was complete."

29
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,500
"The sky's blue...

30
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:34,330
"The sky's blue,
waiting for the rain..."

31
00:02:34,450 --> 00:02:35,450
"And I'm waiting for you..."

32
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:37,500
"And I'm waiting for you..."

33
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:39,700
"The smoke rises slowly..."

34
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,120
"The smoke rises slowly..."

35
00:02:42,290 --> 00:02:43,750
"Across the river, miles away..."

36
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:45,790
"Across the river..."

37
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:48,870
What's wrong, Miss?

38
00:02:48,950 --> 00:02:50,250
What are you reciting?

39
00:02:50,830 --> 00:02:52,290
Is that "Memorial to Emperor"?

40
00:02:55,410 --> 00:02:56,410
The teacher asked you to memorize
"Memorial to Emperor",

41
00:02:56,450 --> 00:02:57,540
not some pop music.

42
00:02:57,790 --> 00:02:58,790
Go stand outside.

43
00:02:58,950 --> 00:02:59,620
Come back in when you've memorized it.

44
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:00,580
Go stand outside.

45
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:02,040
Sheng Shi, you too.

46
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,620
But I've already memorized it.

47
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,000
Didn't you help her?

48
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,700
Help her get it right!

49
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,250
What are you doing?

50
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:25,750
Are you trying to get me in trouble?

51
00:03:28,290 --> 00:03:30,370
I noticed you didn't memorize it,

52
00:03:30,830 --> 00:03:32,660
so I thought you might get lonely

53
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,160
standing outside.

54
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,290
Why are you out here too?

55
00:03:45,450 --> 00:03:47,080
Shwenny, why did you do that?

56
00:03:47,290 --> 00:03:49,330
I'm here because of you!

57
00:03:51,330 --> 00:03:53,040
Think of it as keeping me company.

58
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:59,160
Why do they call you Shwenny?

59
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:05,080
I've got a lot of siblings,

60
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:07,250
so I ended up being the twentieth.

61
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:08,580
Easy to remember, right?

62
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:10,000
Then I'll call you Shwenny too.

63
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:10,910
Okay.

64
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:14,830
Don't look at me.

65
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:26,870
Chu really is cute,

66
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:32,200
even when she's mad.

67
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:37,770
♪Your shadow appears so fast♪

68
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:39,290
Are you okay?

69
00:04:43,410 --> 00:04:44,250
I'm fine.

70
00:04:44,410 --> 00:04:45,700
Thanks for letting me experience

71
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:46,750
what it's like

72
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:48,580
to be completely soaked.

73
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:52,720
♪Cross the line, it's you and me♪

74
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:55,040
♪Softly saying goodbye, set free♪

75
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,850
Did something upset you?

76
00:04:56,850 --> 00:05:00,560
♪Walking paths we once knew♪

77
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:03,040
Yeah,

78
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,620
but after seeing you like this,

79
00:05:04,910 --> 00:05:06,200
I feel a lot better.

80
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:10,290
I knew that would work.

81
00:05:10,970 --> 00:05:14,450
♪I don't want to give up yet♪

82
00:05:14,450 --> 00:05:16,080
If something's bothering you,

83
00:05:16,250 --> 00:05:17,540
you can always talk to me.

84
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:21,750
It's nothing.

85
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,000
Don't you know that women

86
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,450
have a few tough days every month?

87
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:30,180
♪Through the crowd, I hug you tight♪

88
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,620
Just stay warm.

89
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:33,700
I'll pick you up after work,

90
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,000
and we'll head to the Hans together.

91
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:38,560
♪Memories frozen, love so bright♪

92
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:39,950
Shwenny,

93
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,580
we might be a bit late for the party.

94
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:42,790
I just found out

95
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,750
that Lu Yifan met with
the people from Aosi

96
00:05:44,790 --> 00:05:46,250
to talk about a real estate project.

97
00:05:46,370 --> 00:05:47,700
They're signing the deal today.

98
00:05:48,410 --> 00:05:49,540
The Aosi project

99
00:05:49,620 --> 00:05:50,830
is a huge deal

100
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,370
for our company.

101
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:54,250
We can't let Lu Yifan steal it.

102
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,410
Aosi was supposed to

103
00:05:57,540 --> 00:05:59,540
sign with us next week...

104
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:03,120
Lu Yifan must've

105
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:05,160
offered them

106
00:06:05,290 --> 00:06:06,580
a lower price.

107
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:08,080
We've already squeezed our profits down

108
00:06:08,290 --> 00:06:10,580
as much as we can.

109
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:12,290
Unless...

110
00:06:12,450 --> 00:06:13,250
Right.

111
00:06:14,580 --> 00:06:16,700
Unless they're using their usual tricks.

112
00:06:18,290 --> 00:06:20,040
It looks like our decision earlier

113
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,580
was smart.

114
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:23,950
Yes.

115
00:06:24,450 --> 00:06:25,200
They don't know about our connections

116
00:06:25,290 --> 00:06:27,080
with that company.

117
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:29,200
They tried to be sneaky,

118
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:31,540
but I've got some evidence.

119
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:33,040
Nice work.

120
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:37,700
Alright.

121
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:40,700
Get the evidence ready.

122
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:43,000
We're paying Lu Yifan a visit.

123
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,080
No problem.

124
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:08,790
- En, Jiayi.
- Auntie.

125
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:09,290
Auntie.

126
00:07:09,410 --> 00:07:10,290
You're here.

127
00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:11,120
It's great to see you.

128
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:13,540
En, your hairstyle

129
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:15,160
looks gorgeous today.

130
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:21,290
Where's Chengchi?

131
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:22,580
Chengchi's coming to pick me up?

132
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:23,370
Yes.

133
00:07:23,540 --> 00:07:25,040
He saw the weather was bad

134
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,540
and didn't want me to get wet,

135
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:28,160
so he was on his way.

136
00:07:28,790 --> 00:07:30,790
You're so lucky, En,

137
00:07:30,910 --> 00:07:32,950
to have the birthday star
come to pick you up.

138
00:07:33,410 --> 00:07:35,620
Auntie, I didn't know he was coming.

139
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:37,540
I should've told you earlier.

140
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:38,410
It's alright.

141
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:39,290
If he can't find you,

142
00:07:39,370 --> 00:07:40,660
he'll just come back.

143
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,160
Come, get inside.

144
00:07:43,290 --> 00:07:44,500
Have a seat.

145
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,620
I made some sweet bird's nest soup.

146
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,580
I'll get you some.

147
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:48,540
Thank you, Auntie.

148
00:07:48,620 --> 00:07:49,950
- Please sit.
- Thank you, Auntie.

149
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:10,700
En,

150
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,750
can you help me

151
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:12,700
to choose a picture

152
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:13,750
to post?

153
00:08:13,790 --> 00:08:14,660
Sure.

154
00:08:29,890 --> 00:08:31,810
[Your name, my secret.
You are my Chengchi. Am I your Lanshan?]

155
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:35,500
En,

156
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:37,330
wherever you go from now on,

157
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:39,200
I'll always be your safe haven.

158
00:08:40,330 --> 00:08:42,410
A safe haven, huh?

159
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:44,870
Turns out I was the only one

160
00:08:45,410 --> 00:08:47,790
who believed that.

161
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:54,250
En, did you pick?

162
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,790
En?

163
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:58,910
These two are good.

164
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:00,790
These two?

165
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:06,700
Alright.

166
00:09:09,330 --> 00:09:10,330
Mr. Zhang.

167
00:09:15,290 --> 00:09:16,040
Long time no see.

168
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,040
Mr. Sheng.

169
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,080
What brings you here?

170
00:09:19,950 --> 00:09:21,080
What a coincidence, Mr. Sheng.

171
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:22,700
Did you come here to see me?

172
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:23,870
But

173
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,040
I'm about to sign an important contract.

174
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,330
You'll have to wait.

175
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:28,790
What a coincidence.

176
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:31,160
I've got something for you to sign too.

177
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,160
Why, Mr. Sheng?

178
00:09:33,410 --> 00:09:35,040
You here

179
00:09:35,330 --> 00:09:36,750
for my autograph?

180
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:37,790
Mr. Lu,

181
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,660
it's a lawsuit
from one of our subsidiaries

182
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,160
against you.

183
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:43,040
Please sign it.

184
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:44,750
A lawsuit?

185
00:09:44,830 --> 00:09:45,790
What's going on?

186
00:09:49,330 --> 00:09:50,250
It's nothing.

187
00:09:50,410 --> 00:09:52,080
Mr. Zhang, let me explain.

188
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:54,080
One of our subsidiaries

189
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,830
signed a project

190
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:57,500
with Lu Tian Group,

191
00:09:57,750 --> 00:10:00,200
trusting them with the construction.

192
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:02,040
But it turns out

193
00:10:02,950 --> 00:10:05,830
Mr. Lu cut corners on the materials.

194
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,040
What?

195
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:09,500
Mr. Sheng,

196
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:11,290
you can't just straight-up lie.

197
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:13,660
Relax, Mr. Lu.

198
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:15,410
Actually,

199
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:18,000
Mr. Lu has a conscience.

200
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:20,330
He just downgraded

201
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:22,580
the insulation materials
for the exterior walls

202
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:24,410
from A-grade to B2-grade.

203
00:10:24,950 --> 00:10:26,790
As long as nothing major happens,

204
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:28,790
it should be fine.

205
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:30,750
Look,

206
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:32,830
I'm all about honesty,

207
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:35,000
and I really can't stand
the way Mr. Lu does things.

208
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,160
After all,

209
00:10:36,370 --> 00:10:37,540
integrity

210
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:39,700
is what gets you ahead in life,

211
00:10:41,950 --> 00:10:43,290
right, Mr. Lu?

212
00:10:43,450 --> 00:10:44,370
Mr. Sheng,

213
00:10:44,580 --> 00:10:47,000
are you seriously accusing me

214
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:48,910
just because Aosi chose to work with me

215
00:10:48,950 --> 00:10:50,410
instead of you?

216
00:10:50,950 --> 00:10:51,950
Where's your proof?

217
00:10:53,620 --> 00:10:54,950
You think I came here

218
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,660
unprepared?

219
00:10:57,250 --> 00:10:58,370
Sure,

220
00:10:58,540 --> 00:11:00,120
you covered your tracks well

221
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,370
and even bribed the inspectors,

222
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,000
but don't think

223
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:13,540
the Sheng Group

224
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:15,620
is that easy to fool.

225
00:11:21,330 --> 00:11:22,200
Anyway.

226
00:11:23,290 --> 00:11:24,250
Mr. Lu,

227
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:26,870
once you sign, send it over to me.

228
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,000
Mr. Zhang,

229
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:33,290
sorry about

230
00:11:33,540 --> 00:11:34,540
that little hiccup.

231
00:11:34,830 --> 00:11:35,870
You can go ahead.

232
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:38,790
We'll see you in court,

233
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:41,580
Mr. Lu.

234
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,290
You've really disappointed me.

235
00:11:44,450 --> 00:11:45,500
Mr. Sheng.

236
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:19,790
Hello.

237
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:21,910
The person you are trying to reach
is unavailable right now.

238
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,620
Please try again later.

239
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:27,830
Shan.

240
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,040
Chengchi.

241
00:12:31,410 --> 00:12:32,290
It's pouring out here.

242
00:12:32,330 --> 00:12:34,410
- What happened?
- My car broke down.

243
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:35,700
Don't worry about it.

244
00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:37,370
Just get in my car.

245
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:38,370
Sure.

246
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:39,790
Go.

247
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,200
I've got a feeling

248
00:12:51,410 --> 00:12:52,790
Lu Yifan's up to something.

249
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:55,000
Stay sharp

250
00:12:55,370 --> 00:12:56,160
and get ready

251
00:12:56,290 --> 00:12:57,750
for anything.

252
00:12:58,540 --> 00:12:59,370
Got it.

253
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:02,040
How did the meeting go?

254
00:13:02,290 --> 00:13:03,160
All good?

255
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:05,540
From the looks on your faces,

256
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,250
not great.

257
00:13:07,870 --> 00:13:09,290
What did I say?

258
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:11,160
Your intuition's never right.

259
00:13:11,410 --> 00:13:12,160
Don't trust it.

260
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,160
I'm sure

261
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:16,290
something's bothering Shwenny today.

262
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:18,000
Isn't that it?

263
00:13:21,950 --> 00:13:22,830
Are you okay?

264
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:23,660
I'm fine.

265
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,750
Let me make you some cold medicine.

266
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:26,370
Don't bother, Chengchi.

267
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:29,580
En?

268
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:30,580
En.

269
00:13:34,250 --> 00:13:36,040
Why didn't you let me know earlier?
I could've picked you up.

270
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,830
I wanted to surprise you.

271
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,120
Happy birthday.

272
00:13:39,330 --> 00:13:40,290
Thank you.

273
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:44,000
You should dry off.

274
00:13:46,330 --> 00:13:48,500
Shan, take a hot shower

275
00:13:48,830 --> 00:13:49,660
and warm up.

276
00:13:50,250 --> 00:13:51,080
Are you catching a cold?

277
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,370
Next time it rains,

278
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,870
dress warmer.

279
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:01,910
By the way,

280
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:04,250
Shwenny called me earlier

281
00:14:04,540 --> 00:14:05,370
looking for you.

282
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:07,290
I told him I didn't know where you were.

283
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:08,330
It's fine, En.

284
00:14:08,370 --> 00:14:09,830
I talked to him.

285
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:12,160
My car broke down on the way,

286
00:14:12,290 --> 00:14:13,540
but luckily Chengchi showed up.

287
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:14,950
Otherwise, I'd be in a mess.

288
00:14:15,370 --> 00:14:16,500
I was on my way to pick you up

289
00:14:16,620 --> 00:14:17,250
when I ran into her.

290
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:18,580
I'm going to tidy up.

291
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:44,080
