333
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:12,080
Fine.

334
00:17:12,410 --> 00:17:13,910
If it bothers you,

335
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:15,910
I'll keep my distance,

336
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:16,910
