337
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,040
And please,

338
00:17:20,540 --> 00:17:22,370
let's not talk about this anymore.

339
00:17:23,410 --> 00:17:24,790
Shan is part of the Sheng family.

340
00:17:24,910 --> 00:17:26,540
There's nothing between us.

341
00:17:26,660 --> 00:17:28,250
