451
00:22:14,250 --> 00:22:15,830
if that's what you want.

452
00:22:16,660 --> 00:22:17,660
But Gu Lanshan,

453
00:22:17,790 --> 00:22:18,950
can you deny

454
00:22:19,120 --> 00:22:20,540
that you love Chengchi?

455
00:22:21,250 --> 00:22:22,910
Otherwise, how do you explain

456
00:22:23,370 --> 00:22:25,500
knowing he's allergic to crab

457
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:26,700
and writing

458
00:22:26,830 --> 00:22:28,750
those cheesy love lines like

459
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:30,580
"Your name, my secret.

460
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:32,000
You are my Chengchi.

461
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,080
Am I

462
00:22:33,250 --> 00:22:35,330
