469
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,000
En,

470
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:52,290
I swear, I didn't give him that tie.

471
00:22:52,410 --> 00:22:53,750
Gu En,

472
00:22:55,660 --> 00:22:57,330
