478
00:23:09,540 --> 00:23:11,290
If you want me to believe you,

479
00:23:11,450 --> 00:23:13,200
then do it.

480
00:23:13,410 --> 00:23:15,330
Tell Gu Lanshan right now, to her face,

481
00:23:15,450 --> 00:23:17,410
