485
00:23:24,950 --> 00:23:27,410
Me? Crossing the line?

486
00:23:27,790 --> 00:23:28,830
Han Chengchi,

487
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:30,700
we've been together for over 20 years.

488
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:31,950
Don't you know

489
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,370
