514
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:13,330
So,

515
00:25:14,870 --> 00:25:16,500
Miss Gu,

516
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:18,040
if you want to

517
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:19,950
test your man's love,

518
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:22,540
